The evidence with the title 'What the late Stephen Hawking, who studied the Universe's past ... ' says Mar 14, 2018  ... “ we are close to the tipping point where global warming becomes irreversible. Trump 's action [pulling out of the Paris Climate Agreement] could push the Earth over the brink , to become like Venus, with a temperature of two hundred and fifty degrees , and raining sulphuric acid, ” Hawking said. 
